## Academic Use Notice

This project was created as part of a university laboratory assignment in 2017-2018. 
It is intended for educational and portfolio purposes. The implementation may contain 
incomplete features or academic-level code that was appropriate for the learning 
objectives at the time.

Students and educators are welcome to use this code for reference and learning, 
but direct copying for academic submissions would constitute plagiarism.
